description: The DXFtoQET converter is a stand-alone application to convert a Drawing eXchange Format (or "DXF") file -- an ASCII-based, vector-image, CAD data, format file -- into a QElectroTech (or "QET") Element Data (or "ELMT") file which can be opened and edited in the [QElectroTech](https://chocolatey.org/packages/qelectrotech) element editor.
summary: Convert a .DXF file into an .ELMT file
author: Ronny Desmedt,  Laurent Trinques
